high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the round wooden table.
Pick up the closest potato off of the table.
Turn around and walk over to the microwave.

Open the microwave and put the potato inside then close the door and turn on the microwave, after a couple seconds open the microwave back up and remove the now heated potato then close the microwave.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn left to face the counter.
Put the heated potato on the counter to the left of the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato on the counter.

high_descs: turn around, walk forward, turn left to face table
pick up the potato that is on the table
turn around, walk across to the microwave
put the potato in the microwave, turn it on, take potato out when it turns off
take two steps to the right
put the potato on the counter
anns.task_desc: put cooked potato on the counter

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the right side of the kitchen table.
Pick up the potato next to the tomato.
